{"tid":2030872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版國安法之亂》人民日報：為香港裝上「殺毒軟體」，各方不要低估中國的能力和決心","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:15:23.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"926d2164cbd84dcbe53b7159825623ae6020f981","tid":2030872,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2020/05/23/20200523-100211_U720_M613580_16bb.jpg?itok=zWkpv2UD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F05%2F23%2F20200523-100211_U720_M613580_16bb.jpg%3Fitok%3DzWkpv2UD&h=da1fa1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國政府決定推動「港版國安法」立法，讓國安機構直接進駐香港，企圖徹底扼殺香港的民主自由，也為「一國兩制」敲響喪鐘。官媒《人民日報》23日發文恫嚇，聲稱北京此舉是為香港裝上「殺毒軟體」，警告「反中亂港勢力」不要低估中國政府處理香港問題的能力和決心<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》表示，2019年香港發生「修例風波」（反送中），反中亂港勢力膽大妄為，外部反華勢力黑手頻出，嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線，損害法治、國家主權、安全、發展利益，必須採取有力措施依法予以防範制止，避免香港淪為「不設防」的城市，這是全國人大出手進行相關立法的現實背景和內在邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》聲稱，「港版國安法」不會影響香港居民依法享有的各項權利和自由，只有反中亂港分子和外部反華勢力會受影響，各方的批評恰恰說明人大相關立法是當務之急，正中要害。（相關報導：北京強推「港版國安法」閹割一國兩制 香港特首林鄭月娥：全力支持、全力配合｜更多文章）<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》強調，港獨不除、外部反華勢力不逐，香港不能安寧。「港版國安法」就是要為香港裝上加強版「殺毒軟體」，築牢「一國兩制」的制度根基。任何反中亂港勢力，切莫低估中國政府處理香港問題的能力和決心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2673127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2673127&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=9387fc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2673127</a><br />\n裝番個衛士360壓壓驚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3622894a29274299c54903093a604433cd85e8","tid":2030872,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"hao123"},{"pid":"c6dd9cfeff7d044ec7a780e9bb108896fd23a1f2","tid":2030872,"uid":173179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"屌好撚驚<br />\n裝返個360先"},{"pid":"e753725453a5bb6152122181620890985f3d02aa","tid":2030872,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/L%C3%BCba_Filtered.png/revision/latest?cb=20090619091919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FL%25C3%25BCba_Filtered.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20090619091919&h=44e72e1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45aec49ac124a2f460c33efbb1e743c1136a89a6","tid":2030872,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaPrgPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaPrgPJ.png&h=f68b5351&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d35b2c98bc0be5d9ad6b2d8f2debf26b04e1fd1","tid":2030872,"uid":102119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"以為老納回來了"},{"pid":"b4fe3e717b4f950c40b1e4ca3d2654b21a8b6afb","tid":2030872,"uid":85694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"唔講以為香港人奪咗權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205e308a0eaba08feb2837db42ab6ee06f6d4e1c","tid":2030872,"uid":31330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"即時諗起360<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比病毒更似病毒反而自稱防毒軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe354b9e32369e2ef1a070acbb4fb79da071cf8","tid":2030872,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ahkmBa.jpg